2 Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska; to authorize the operation of
3 all-terrain vehicles and utility-type vehicles between the hours of
4 sunset and sunrise if used for snow removal as prescribed; to
5 harmonize provisions; and to repeal the original section.
